00:02:39.030 --> 00:02:42.400
AxonVR wants you to feel virtual reality.

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:48.650
The HaptX is a haptic textile that can provide
vibration, tactile and thermal feedback for

00:02:48.650 --> 00:02:52.239
feeling virtual shape, texture, weight and
temperature.

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:56.930
They claim the range of touch varies from
the brush of a butterfly’s wing to the impact

00:02:56.930 --> 00:03:02.169
of a punch and the goal is for their system
to be available in theme parks and arcades

00:03:02.169 --> 00:03:04.769
and not likely in your house.

