00:04:01.819 --> 00:04:06.579
EnChroma are glasses designed to alleviate
red-green color blindness.

00:04:06.579 --> 00:04:12.470
The lenses feature a patent pending multinotch
filter which cut out sharp wavelength of light

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:17.470
to enhance specific colors and separate the
red and green cones.

00:04:17.470 --> 00:04:22.070
This helps to counter the overlap between
red and green which affects those with that

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:23.630
form of color blindness.

00:04:23.630 --> 00:04:28.920
They allow people, for instance to easily
identify the color difference between a green

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:31.340
traffic light from a blue sky background.

